The BlobCity DB
=====================

Running
-------
To start the database on Mac OS, UNIX, GNU/Linux:
./bin/blobcity.sh

(Currently no queryCode-line parameters are supported)


Requirements
------------
A directory named "/blobcity" will be created in your root directory on first execution. If you do not want to create 
this file in your root directory, create a symbolic link to another location before starting the database.

(Support for an interactive startup will be added in the future for setting up the initial configuration)

Supported filesystems:
HFS+ (MacOS)
XFS (GNU/Linux, other UNIX)


Default Credentials
-------------------
username: root
password: root


Further reading
---------------
Please visit: http://docs.blobcity.com/

